%hive
-- Every tripâ€™s aggregated features at a trip id level.
--
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS drive_features
STORED AS PARQUET LOCATION 'hdfs:///user/hive/warehouse/drive_features' TBLPROPERTIES ("parquet.compression"="SNAPPY")
AS SELECT deaccel_event_cnt.trip_id AS trip_id,
    deaccel_event_cnt.ft_count_vehicle_deaccel_val AS ft_count_vehicle_deaccel_val,
    hard_brake_10_cnt.ft_sum_hard_brakes_10_flg_val AS ft_sum_hard_brakes_10_flg_val,
    hard_brake_3_cnt.ft_sum_hard_brakes_3_flg_val AS ft_sum_hard_brakes_3_flg_val,
    sum_deaccel_cnt.ft_sum_time_deaccel_val AS ft_sum_time_deaccel_val,
    accel_event_cnt.ft_count_vehicle_accel_val AS ft_count_vehicle_accel_val,
    hard_accel_10_cnt.ft_sum_hard_accel_10_flg_val AS ft_sum_hard_accel_10_flg_val,
    hard_accel_3_cnt.ft_sum_hard_accel_3_flg_val AS ft_sum_hard_accel_3_flg_val,
    sum_accel_cnt.ft_sum_time_accel_val AS ft_sum_time_accel_val
FROM (
    SELECT trip_id, COUNT(*) AS ft_count_vehicle_deaccel_val
    FROM (
        SELECT trip_id, acceleration_group
        FROM drive_temp
        GROUP BY trip_id, acceleration_group
        HAVING MIN(acceleration) < 0
    ) deaccel_event
    GROUP BY trip_id
) deaccel_event_cnt
LEFT OUTER JOIN (
    SELECT trip_id, COUNT(*) AS ft_sum_hard_brakes_10_flg_val
    FROM (
        SELECT trip_id, acceleration_group
        FROM drive_temp
        GROUP BY trip_id, acceleration_group
        HAVING MIN(acceleration) <= -10
    ) hard_break_10
    GROUP BY trip_id
) hard_brake_10_cnt
ON deaccel_event_cnt.trip_id = hard_brake_10_cnt.trip_id
LEFT OUTER JOIN (
    SELECT trip_id, COUNT(*) AS ft_sum_hard_brakes_3_flg_val
    FROM (
        SELECT trip_id, acceleration_group, MIN(acceleration) AS min_acceleration
        FROM drive_temp
        GROUP BY trip_id, acceleration_group
        HAVING MIN(acceleration) <= -3 AND MIN(acceleration) > -10
    ) hard_break_3
    GROUP BY trip_id
) hard_brake_3_cnt
ON deaccel_event_cnt.trip_id = hard_brake_3_cnt.trip_id
LEFT OUTER JOIN (
    SELECT trip_id, COUNT(*) AS ft_sum_time_deaccel_val
    FROM (
        SELECT trip_id, acceleration, acceleration_group
        FROM drive_temp
        WHERE acceleration < 0
    ) sum_deaccel
    GROUP BY trip_id
) sum_deaccel_cnt
ON deaccel_event_cnt.trip_id = sum_deaccel_cnt.trip_id
LEFT OUTER JOIN (
    SELECT trip_id, COUNT(*) AS ft_count_vehicle_accel_val
    FROM (
        SELECT trip_id, acceleration_group
        FROM drive_temp
        GROUP BY trip_id, acceleration_group
        HAVING MAX(acceleration) > 0
    ) accel_event
    GROUP BY trip_id
) accel_event_cnt
ON deaccel_event_cnt.trip_id = accel_event_cnt.trip_id
LEFT OUTER JOIN (
    SELECT trip_id, COUNT(*) AS ft_sum_hard_accel_10_flg_val
    FROM (
        SELECT trip_id, acceleration_group
        FROM drive_temp
        GROUP BY trip_id, acceleration_group
        HAVING MAX(acceleration) >= 10
    ) hard_accel_10
    GROUP BY trip_id
) hard_accel_10_cnt
ON deaccel_event_cnt.trip_id = hard_accel_10_cnt.trip_id
LEFT OUTER JOIN (
    SELECT trip_id, COUNT(*) AS ft_sum_hard_accel_3_flg_val
    FROM (
        SELECT trip_id, acceleration_group, MIN(acceleration) AS min_acceleration
        FROM drive_temp
        GROUP BY trip_id, acceleration_group
        HAVING MAX(acceleration) >= 3 AND MAX(acceleration) < 10
    ) hard_accel_3
    GROUP BY trip_id
) hard_accel_3_cnt
ON deaccel_event_cnt.trip_id = hard_accel_3_cnt.trip_id
LEFT OUTER JOIN (
    SELECT trip_id, COUNT(*) AS ft_sum_time_accel_val
    FROM (
        SELECT trip_id, acceleration, acceleration_group
        FROM drive_temp
        WHERE acceleration > 0
    ) sum_accel
    GROUP BY trip_id
) sum_accel_cnt
ON deaccel_event_cnt.trip_id = sum_accel_cnt.trip_id
ORDER BY trip_id
